      <title>NekoAtsume游戏数据</title>
      <link href="/2019/11/24/nekoatsume/"/>
      <url>/2019/11/24/nekoatsume/</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<link rel="stylesheet" class="aplayer-secondary-style-marker" href="\assets\css\APlayer.min.css"><script src="\assets\js\APlayer.min.js" class="aplayer-secondary-script-marker"></script><script class="meting-secondary-script-marker" src="\assets\js\Meting.min.js"></script><ul><li>本文翻译自<a href="https://www.reddit.com/r/nekoatsume/comments/3sbgce/i_made_a_spreadsheet_charting_fish_income_for/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">I made a spreadsheet charting fish income for each toy and cat </a></li></ul><p><strong>注意：</strong>各排行中的数据为特定食物下的特殊值，依据使用食物的不同，该数值会对应的上升或下降。</p><h2 id="黄金小鱼干生产效率最高的小型设施"><a href="#黄金小鱼干生产效率最高的小型设施" class="headerlink" title="黄金小鱼干生产效率最高的小型设施"></a>黄金小鱼干生产效率最高的小型设施</h2><div class="table-container"><table><thead><tr><th style="text-align:center">排名</th><th style="text-align:center">名称</th><th style="text-align:center">价格</th><th style="text-align:center">效率</th><th style="text-align:center">图片</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td style="text-align:center"><font color=gold>1</font></td><td style="text-align:center">西式靠垫(绿)</td><td style="text-align:center">100普通小鱼干</td><td style="text-align:center">4.3黄金小鱼干/天</td><td style="text-align:center"><img src= data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODdhAQABAPAAAMPDwwAAACwAAAAAAQABAAACAkQBADs= data-src="https://vignette.wikia.nocookie.net/nekoatsume/images/0/02/Cushion_green.png/revision/latest/scale-to-width-down/100?cb=20151106175628"></td></tr><tr><td style="text-align:center"><font color=silver>2</font></td><td style="text-align:center">橘色方块</td><td style="text-align:center">100普通小鱼干</td><td style="text-align:center">4.0黄金小鱼干/天</td><td style="text-align:center"><img src= data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODdhAQABAPAAAMPDwwAAACwAAAAAAQABAAACAkQBADs= data-src="https://vignette.wikia.nocookie.net/nekoatsume/images/5/5a/Cube_orange.png/revision/latest?cb=20151106175646"></td></tr><tr><td style="text-align:center"><font color=bronze>3</font></td><td style="text-align:center">西式靠垫(黄)</td><td style="te